rows.label: tev036101_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Yuyu if anything is troubling her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036101_MSG0001
rows.name:
My job is to decide how to divide the cargo up among
the Ma-non, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036101_MSG0002
rows.name:
...Oh, you want to know what's inside? Machines, silly.
They've all been sent here from NLA, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036101_MSG0003
rows.name:
Some need repairing or upgrading, you see?
But the city wants us to to repurpose others into new
inventions.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036101_MSG0004
rows.name:
And that's why my job is so important, I guess?
If I don't get the machines to Ma-non with the right
qualifications, we'd have a disaster on our hands, no?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036101_MSG0010
rows.name:
Nothing makes me happier than enjoying a a nice
grenade pizza with my sweetheart Ackwar, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036101_MSG0013
rows.name:
Unfortunately, we don't get much time as a couple
these days because of all the work BLADE dumps
on him, you see?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036101_MSG0014
rows.name:
But while I miss him, I know he's busy making a
difference, isn't he? So he needs my my support...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036101_MSG0015
rows.name:
...What's the phrase you use? I need to corner him?
No, wait. I need to be IN his corner![ST:wait ]
